node_6.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, go to the library at Oak Hill College to work on his research paper at 8:00 am, have lunch at Hobbs Cafe at 12:00 pm, return to the library to work on the research paper until 5:00 pm, have dinner at Hobbs Cafe at 5:00 pm, continue working on the research paper until 7:00 pm, relax and watch some TV for an hour from 7 to 8 pm, reflect on the day and plan for the following day from 8 to 9 pm.
